1. Isusa sam pronašao u šumi. (*Isusa* - subject) (I found a squirrel in the forest.)
2. Izašao sam iz kuće i ugledao *isusu*. (*Isusu* - direct object) (I left the house and saw a squirrel.)
3. Isusa *sam* nahranio orašastim plodovima. (*Sam* - emphasized auxiliary verb) (I personally fed the squirrel with nuts.)
4. Često se igram sa *isusom*. (*Isusom* - instrumental case) (I often play with the squirrel.)
5. Vidio sam *isuse* kako skakuću po drveću. (*Isuse* - plural form) (I saw squirrels jumping from tree to tree.)